    <name>MXP-L1 — Dolomites Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from MXP and ride into the Dolomites. Hit Brescia and Passo del Tonale — 1884m. Loop back to MXP over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
